WEBVTT

00:00:00.992 --> 00:00:02.445
So here we are.

00:00:02.469 --> 00:00:05.524
I'm at home, as I'm sure
many of you are, too.

00:00:05.548 --> 00:00:07.633
And we've all begun to understand

00:00:07.657 --> 00:00:09.712
how our relationship with ourselves,

00:00:09.736 --> 00:00:10.903
with each other

00:00:10.927 --> 00:00:12.224
and the spaces we exist in

00:00:12.248 --> 00:00:15.669
can deeply impact
our sense of identity and purpose.

00:00:15.693 --> 00:00:18.542
So much has dramatically changed.

00:00:18.566 --> 00:00:21.936
There's a sense of distance now
unlike ever before.

00:00:21.960 --> 00:00:23.516
But what if I told you

00:00:23.540 --> 00:00:27.904
that you could find a way
from your heart to your hand

00:00:27.928 --> 00:00:29.829
to reconnect again,

00:00:29.853 --> 00:00:33.861
and that through this practice
and embracing this cause,